    BANKING SERVICES

    This integral feature provides seamless access to fundamental financial services in remote regions. Users can open savings accounts, transfer funds, and apply for loans through a user-friendly digital platform. By bridging the gap between unbanked areas and traditional banking, this service empowers communities with the tools to manage their finances securely and conveniently.
